31T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"市場有一百個蘋果<br />\n<br />\n1. 商人（沽空機構）有好強既信譽，唔駛借到貨係手都已經賣到俾人，所以佢可以借都唔借就出現左額外第一百零一個蘋果<br />\n<br />\n2. 商人問其他人（股份持有人）借蘋果，然後賣左俾其他買家，呢d買家再借俾商人又再賣出去，同一個蘋果不停借俾人再賣，數值上就多過100<br />\n<br />\n唔知啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n類似啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cf851a50f5a905294d466a52ec8739dbb73e6c","tid":2388354,"uid":291491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:55:47.000Z","msg":"同佢講賺緊錢 SH就得架啦  解釋咁多做乜"},{"pid":"c94712ca9b9fbee946c7ccc84fd5497957537b81","tid":2388354,"uid":87557,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"啱啱解咗三四個字佢明咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢解極我都唔明咩叫越位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b777213148abebac7ac1e456adf829bb6d0279b","tid":2388354,"uid":138489,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:00:30.000Z","msg":"我同身邊幾個女仔friend都喺度SH<br />\n反而條仔唔明我哋搞緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865d9f7673cf72443576918e8d8cf8705214b511","tid":2388354,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c94712ca9b9fbee946c7ccc84fd5497957537b81","tid":2388354,"uid":87557,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"啱啱解咗三四個字佢明咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢解極我都唔明咩叫越位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:00:30.000Z","msg":"巴打反而係你唔明越位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35cd587375b37cce696ee9e620727ae93742e05","tid":2388354,"uid":87557,"l